      <t>&lt;p&gt;This note describes some theoretically-possible failure modes for TCP connections and discusses possible remedies.  In particular, one very simple fix is identified.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
